CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 9, 1953, pg. 34, reads: "At Kingsley House 'Come And See Night' - When Kingsley House held its 'Come and See Night' at the East End Community Center Tuesday night, one of the dance numbers performed by the young girls was based on a tight-rope act. Shown above during the 'Tight-Rope Dancing' number were: Brenda Wilson, Sylvia Taylor, and Jackie Dennis.... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Brenda Wilson, Sylvia Taylor, and Jackie Dennis holding umbrellas and performing tight- rope dance act at Kingsley House "Come and See Night" program at East End Community Center
